reviewText: Great show!  Great family!  Too bad it was cancelled.
Very disappointed since I haven't been able to watch it because the dvd cannot be used in the dvd players actually on sale in London and Europe.
Love the show! The dvd's are great quality and packaged well. Super, Super fast shipping on Amazon's part. Thanks for everything.

Good show with good moral stories.  Show that with some work, you make it on your own.

When is Season 2 & 3 coming out???

Best show out there.... great for the whole family it's not about the stupid drama and yelling screaming and fighting. It shows that even when bad things happen you need to find the good.

I bought these Dvds and it was shipped fast and had no problems at all.
